<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #4A90E2; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .footer { background: #f1f1f1; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
        .info-box { background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #4A90E2; }
        .file-list { background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .file-item { padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
        .highlight { color: #4A90E2; font-weight: bold; }
        .warning { background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>‚úì Receipt Confirmation</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>

            <p>This is to confirm that we have successfully received your email and are processing the attached documents.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Email Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Received:</strong> {{receivedAt}}</p>
                <p><strong>From:</strong> {{fromAddress}}</p>
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {{subject}}</p>
                <p><strong>Tracking ID:</strong> <code>{{correlationId}}</code></p>
            </div>

            <div class="file-list">
                <h3>Validated Documents</h3>
                <p>The following <span class="highlight">{{processedAttachments}}</span> file(s) matched our processing rules and will be extracted:</p>

                {{#attachments}}
                <div class="file-item">
                    üìÑ <strong>{{filename}}</strong>
                    {{#size}}<span style="color: #999;"> ({{size}})</span>{{/size}}
                </div>
                {{/attachments}}

                {{^attachments}}
                <p><em>No valid documents found in this email.</em></p>
                {{/attachments}}
            </div>

            {{#hasRejected}}
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Note:</strong> {{totalAttachments}} attachment(s) were received, but only {{processedAttachments}} matched processing rules. Unmatched files were ignored.
            </div>
            {{/hasRejected}}

            <p>You will receive another notification once the extraction process is complete.</p>

            <p><em>If you believe any expected document is missing from the list above, please re-send the email or contact our support team.</em></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Atina ‚Äì Email Converter</strong></p>
            <p>Automated document processing system | <strong>{{tenantName}}</strong></p>
            <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #999;">Email ID: {{emailId}} | Correlation ID: {{correlationId}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
